---
title: All-American Crispy Chicken Bites with Garlic Rice, Celery Slaw & Smokey Aioli
description: Chomp down on these delectable chicken bites, easy to eat and easy to make. Fry them up in our powerhouse AllAmerican spice and wait for the magic to begin when you drizzle over some smokey aioli. If you want a bit of crunch, pair it with a celery slaw. Time to get chewing!
